$(function(){function e(){var e=$("#txtLatitude").val();var t=$("#txtAltitude").val();var n=$("#cmbUnits").val();if(e!=""&&t!=""&&n!=""){var r=new gravity;if(n=="ft")t=r.changeToMetres(t);r.setLocation(e,0,t);var i=r.getGravity();switch(i){case 0:$("#lblResult").html("Latitude not valid");break;case 1:$("#lblResult").html("Height above Everest?");break;case 2:$("#lblResult").html("Height below Dead Sea?");break;default:if(n=="m")$("#lblResult").html(i.toFixed(3)+" m/s&#178;");else $("#lblResult").html(r.changeToFeet(i).toFixed(3)+" ft/s&#178;");break}}}jQuery("#lblResult").fitText();$("#txtAltitude,#txtLatitude").focusout(function(){e()});$("#cmbUnits").change(function(){e()})})